title: [Orcswold, Low Moors]
description: The fields spread out into a low, boggy field to the south, featureless except for a grassy mound of earth that rises from the flat landscape just to the south.  No creatures seem to have built their nests here, and a flicker of odd, crackling energy, like a nearby storm, passes through the air.
